data.description: Tons of flex space! Primary bedroom has ensuite sitting area for cozy movie nights, reading escapes or home office. Walk-in closets throughout. Versatile upstairs and downstairs living areas create the perfect setting for homeschooling, game rooms, workout oasis, library, home office. Move-in-ready, EV wired garage, new HVAC systems, stove, range hood, fence, carpeting, fresh paint (2023) Remodeled oversized primary shower, new front & back doors (2022) New oven, sink, garbage disposal, microwave (2021) New roof (2020) Community pools, clubhouse & playgrounds. Three lakes within 3.8 miles! Imagine summer days, swimming, boating and fishing, creating lifelong memories. Picture the tranquil neighborhood 6-mile paved walking and biking loop around lake. Less than 7 miles from downtown Fort Worth and the Stockyards where you can enjoy authentic Texas culture with dancing, shopping, delicious meals, stock shows, and weekly rodeos. Come and see how this house outshines the competition.
